data.description: Custom built home overlooking the city sitting on .63 acres! This home features a spacious primary suite on the main floor, solar panels installed last year, and space for all your toys! You are greeted by a large living room with high ceilings and a fireplace to gather around. The backyard has a pavered patio area and room to roam with mature trees, storage shed, and a greenhouse that can stay or be removed.
